If you have worked for large organisations, you will have come across the competency model. You will have discovered that humans are ranked according to a pre-set group of competencies, or qualities that you are meant to demonstrate in order to excel in your job. 

What are these competencies? 

Things like customer focus, teamwork, goal orientation, business acumen, technical skills, strategic thinking and the like. 



